<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>404 – Page Not Found · ShoeZone</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <style>
      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      :root {
        --black: #0a0a0a;
        --white: #ffffff;
        --off-white: #f7f6f3;
        --grey-100: #e8e8e6;
        --grey-200: #d0cfcc;
        --grey-400: #9a9a96;
        --grey-600: #6b6b68;
        --grey-800: #2b2b28;
      }

      html,
      body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
        background: var(--black);
        color: var(--white);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      /* Dot-grid texture */
      body::before {
        content: "";
        position: fixed;
        inset: 0;
        background-image: radial-gradient(
            circle at 70% 30%,
            rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) 0%,
            transparent 55%
          ),
          radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: auto, 28px 28px;
        pointer-events: none;
        z-index: 0;
      }

      .error-page {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      /* Giant background number */
      .error-bg-num {
        font-family: "Bebas Neue", sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(160px, 28vw, 340px);
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        line-height: 1;
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        pointer-events: none;
        user-select: none;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .error-icon {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      .error-code {
        font-family: "Bebas Neue", sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
        letter-spacing: 0.25em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
        margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
      }

      .error-title {
        font-family: "Bebas Neue", sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        color: var(--white);
        line-height: 1;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .error-desc {
        font-size: clamp(0.88rem, 1.5vw, 1rem);
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
        max-width: 380px;
        line-height: 1.65;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      }

      .error-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .btn-primary-error {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        padding: 0.85rem 2.25rem;
        background: var(--white);
        color: var(--black);
        border: none;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        text-decoration: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
        font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
      }
      .btn-primary-error:hover {
        background: var(--off-white);
        transform: translateY(-1px);
        color: var(--black);
      }

      .btn-ghost-error {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        padding: 0.85rem 2.25rem;
        background: transparent;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
        border: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        text-decoration: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
        font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
      }
      .btn-ghost-error:hover {
        border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      }

      /* Logo top-left */
      .error-logo {
        position: fixed;
        top: 1.5rem;
        left: 1.75rem;
        font-family: "Bebas Neue", sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
        text-decoration: none;
        z-index: 2;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }
      .error-logo:hover {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      }

      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .error-actions {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
        }
        .btn-primary-error,
        .btn-ghost-error {
          width: 100%;
          max-width: 280px;
          justify-content: center;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <a href="/" class="error-logo">ShoeZone</a>

    <div class="error-bg-num">404</div>

    <div class="error-page">
      <div class="error-icon"><i class="fas fa-shoe-prints"></i></div>
      <div class="error-code">Error 404</div>
      <h1 class="error-title">Page Not Found</h1>
      <p class="error-desc">
        Looks like this page took a wrong turn. It may have been moved, deleted, or the URL might be
        incorrect.
      </p>
      <div class="error-actions">
        <a href="/" class="btn-primary-error"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Back to Home</a>
        <a href="/products" class="btn-ghost-error"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Shop Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
